Quickstrike made it down from the ladder and looked around. It was nearly 
pitch black. "It's th' bunker where Black Arachnia and Tarantulas suppose t' 
be," he replied to Dark Mouse. He actived his infra-red vision.

"Sugar-bot? Tarantulas? Ya here?" he called out.
